{"tid":584862,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民瘋傳】「最完美樹熊」現身 澳洲民眾讚可愛︰識笑咁嘅","createTime":"2018-03-08T06:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T13:12:11.000Z","uid":109136,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"91359cd5c54788e64ec4c35c739a023e1e87cc3d","tid":584862,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/145929_d19ae84e07f7edd11a19ee0ef3b9646b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F145929_d19ae84e07f7edd11a19ee0ef3b9646b.jpg&h=a3c1ffe4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n澳洲阿德萊德有民眾無意中在路邊遇到一隻可愛樹熊，連忙拍下牠的身影並上載到社交網，大讚牠「完美得過份」，引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n照片中的樹熊「眼仔碌碌」望著鏡頭，似乎還露出了害羞的笑容，被冠上「完美」稱號當然不只靠眼睛和笑容，網民也大讚牠身上豐滿漂亮的毛髮造型「無得彈」。<br />\n拍攝到可愛樹熊的網民在社交網上表示，她是在阿德萊德洛夫蒂山看到牠，「這是最完美的樹熊」，地點距離市區只有十分鐘路程<br />\n網民紛紛交流遇到樹熊的經驗，有人說見過樹熊跑進他家花園，有人則說阿德萊德有許多不錯的野生動物，「搬去墨爾本就只有那些爛鳥和恐怖的爬蟲」。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180228&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57885971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180228%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57885971&d=KQPkIZW%2B%2FEF3KFCtQifZAzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6c60f1da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180228%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57885971&h=97a67219\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180228&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57885971</a>"},{"pid":"92e2d28daa9a45479a8530a6c126e2b2f66b896f","tid":584862,"uid":139671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"閱✅"},{"pid":"c48841bc56d33b78409e9b7ed3a5a72636c6e020","tid":584862,"uid":24961,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"